text
@d1 1
a1 1
NEG        Negate (invert contraast) an image                      NEG      
d4 4
a7 4
PURPOSE:  Performs arithmetic negation point for point on the
           input image to create an output image, then adds the 
           original image maximum (FMAX) to each pixel so that origin
           is now zero.
d9 2
a10 1
SEE ALSO: AR  (Arithmetic operation on an image)
